query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(question tag_question site) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tag_question
inner join question AS question
on tag_question.question_id = question.id
inner join site AS site
on question.site_id = site.site_id AND tag_question.site_id = site.site_id AND site.site_name = 'pt'
inner join tag AS tag
on tag.site_id = site.site_id AND tag_question.tag_id = tag.id AND tag.name = 'ckeditor';
